<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Rule: design_functional_unit_allocation_to_assembly_component_constraint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Functional_decomposition_to_design_mim.design_functional_unit_allocation_to_assembly_component_constraint">
The <b>design_functional_unit_allocation_to_assembly_component_constraint</b> rule
constrains the relating and related <express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition"/> for a
<express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship.relating_product_definition"/> :<express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship.related_product_definition"/> 
<express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship"/> when it is used as a design functional unit
allocation to assembly_component.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Functional_decomposition_to_design_mim.design_functional_unit_allocation_to_assembly_component_constraint.wr:WR1">
IF <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship.relating_product_definition"/> :<express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship.related_product_definition"/>
<express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship"/>.name =
'design functional unit allocation to assembly component' the
SELF.<express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship.relating_product_definition"/> shall have a description = 'design definition path'
and an id = 'design composition path'.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Functional_decomposition_to_design_mim.design_functional_unit_allocation_to_assembly_component_constraint.wr:WR2">
IF <express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship.relating_product_definition"/> :<express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship.related_product_definition"/>
<express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship"/>.name = 
'design functional unit allocation to assembly component' the 
SELF.<express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship.related_product_definition"/> shall be a <express_ref linkend="physical_unit_design_view:mim:Physical_unit_design_view_mim.component_definition"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Rule: design_functional_unit_allocation_to_assembly_component_unique_constraint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Functional_decomposition_to_design_mim.design_functional_unit_allocation_to_assembly_component_unique_constraint">
The <b>design_functional_unit_allocation_to_assembly_component_unique_constraint</b> rule
constrains <express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship.relating_product_definition"/> :<express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship.related_product_definition"/>
<express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship"/> population members, that fill the role
of ARM <express_ref linkend="Functional_decomposition_to_design:arm:Functional_decomposition_to_design_arm.Design_functional_unit_allocation_to_assembly_component"/>, so that the
combination of ARM <express_ref linkend="Functional_decomposition_to_design:arm:Functional_decomposition_to_design_arm.Design_functional_unit_allocation_to_assembly_component.implementation"/> and ARM <express_ref linkend="Functional_decomposition_to_design:arm:Functional_decomposition_to_design_arm.Design_functional_unit_allocation_to_assembly_component.path_alias"/> shall be unique within the population.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Functional_decomposition_to_design_mim.design_functional_unit_allocation_to_assembly_component_unique_constraint.wr:WR1">
Every instance of <express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship.relating_product_definition"/> :<express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship.related_product_definition"/>
<express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship"/> with a name of
'design functional unit allocation to assembly component' must have a
unique combination <express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship.related_product_definition"/> and id attributes.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Rule: reference_composition_path_constraint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Functional_decomposition_to_design_mim.reference_composition_path_constraint">
The <b>reference_composition_path_constraint</b> rule constrains the related and
relating <express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition"/> of a <express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship.relating_product_definition"/> :<express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship.related_product_definition"/>
<express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship"/> when it is
a reference composition path.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Functional_decomposition_to_design_mim.reference_composition_path_constraint.wr:WR1">
IF <express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship.relating_product_definition"/> :<express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship.related_product_definition"/>
<express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship"/>.name = 'reference composition path' 
THEN SELF.<express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship.relating_product_definition"/> shall be a <express_ref linkend="network_functional_design_view:mim:Network_functional_design_view_mim.component_functional_unit"/> 
whose {description = 'reference definition path'} 
{<express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.p
roduct_definition.frame_of_reference"/>.name = 'functional occurrence'}.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Functional_decomposition_to_design_mim.reference_composition_path_constraint.wr:WR2">
IF <express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship.relating_product_definition"/> :<express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship.related_product_definition"/>
<express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship"/>.name = 'reference composition path' 
THEN SELF.<express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship.related_product_definition"/> shall be a <express_ref linkend="network_functional_design_view:mim:Network_functional_design_view_mim.component_functional_unit"/> 
whose <express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.p
roduct_definition.frame_of_reference"/>.name = 'functional occurrence'.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Rule: reference_functional_unit_assignment_to_part_constraint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Functional_decomposition_to_design_mim.reference_functional_unit_assignment_to_part_constraint">
The <b>reference_functional_unit_assignment_to_part_constraint</b> rule constrains
the use of product_to_part_relationship when it is used as a reference 
functional unit assignment to part.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Functional_decomposition_to_design_mim.reference_functional_unit_assignment_to_part_constraint.wr:WR1">
If a product_to_part_relationship has a name of 
'reference functional unit assignment to part' then the 
<express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship.related_product_definition"/> shall be a <express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition"/> with a 
<express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition.frame_of_reference"/> that is an <express_ref linkend="application_context_schema:ir_express:application_context_schema.application_context_element"/> with a name 
of 'physical design', or 'physical design usage'.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Functional_decomposition_to_design_mim.reference_functional_unit_assignment_to_part_constraint.wr:WR2">
If a product_to_part_relationship has a name of 
'reference functional unit assignment to part' then the 
<express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_relationship.relating_product_definition"/> shall be a <express_ref 
linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition"/> with a 
description of 'design definition path' and an id of 
'reference composition path'.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Rule: reference_functional_unit_assignment_to_part_unique_constraint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Functional_decomposition_to_design_mim.reference_functional_unit_assignment_to_part_unique_constraint">
The <b>reference_functional_unit_assignment_to_part_unique_constraint</b> rule constrains <express_ref 
linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/>
population members, that fill the role of ARM <express_ref linkend="Functional_decomposition_to_design:arm:Functional_decomposition_to_design_arm.Reference_functional_unit_assignment_to_part"/>, to have
unique <express_ref linkend="Functional_decomposition_to_design:arm:Functional_decomposition_to_design_arm.Reference_functional_unit_assignment_to_part.implementation">implementations</express_ref> on each <express_ref linkend="Functional_decomposition_to_design:arm:Functional_decomposition_to_design_arm.Reference_functional_unit_assignment_to_part.path_alias"/>.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Functional_decomposition_to_design_mim.reference_functional_unit_assignment_to_part_unique_constraint.wr:WR1">
Every instance of <express_ref 
linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/> with a name of 'reference
functional unit assignment to part' that has a common description must have
unique <express_ref 
linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship.related_shape_aspect"/>.<express_ref 
linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect.of_shape"/>.definition attribute values.
</ext_description>

</ext_descriptions>
